shorewall-nft (1.4.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Release 1.4.0: DNS-driven nft-set population (dnstap + PBDNSMessage
    pipelines, DnsSetTracker, SetWriter, StateStore, ReloadMonitor,
    WorkerRouter, HA peer-link replication) and Prometheus metrics
    exporter beta (NftCollector, LinkCollector, CtCollector; :9748).
  * See CHANGELOG.md for full details.

